    PersistenceManager, RemotePersistenceManager
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RestADFBCXMLPersistenceManager

    public class RestXMLPersistenceManager
extends RestPersistenceManager
    Implementation of Persistence manager interface that provides basic CRUD operations using the REST web services protocol against a remote server. The payload of the REST web service should be in XML format.
